                           Wienn</rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="#pe__ulrich_churtzman_QGW_II_I_294"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Ulreichs tochter des
                           Chu/orczmans, <roleName type="dead">dem got genad</roleName></rs></rs>
                  </rs>,<triggerstring n="disp">setzt</triggerstring><rs type="fn" role="recipient"> ihren
